OL,7,FAkeel Nanawaba, Hannaa Vorajee, and
OL,8,Ftheir four-year-old daughter Sara were
OL,9,Fon their way home to Gloucester after
OL,10,Fa surprise visit to India. Then
OL,11,Fdisaster struck.
OL,13,FTheir family is devastated by their
OL,14,Floss, after the Air India plane they
OL,15,Fwere flying on crashed in Ahmedabad.
OL,17,FThe aircraft struck a medical college
OL,18,Fhostel in a residential part of
OL,19,FAhmedabad, killing 241 of the 242
OL,20,Fpeople on board, 52 of whom were
OL,21,FBritish.
