OL,7,FSpeaking of little Sara, Hannaa's
OL,8,Fbrother Mohammed Vorajee, says "She
OL,9,Fwasn't just my niece, she was my
OL,10,Feverything.
OL,12,F"She was the life of both of our
OL,13,Ffamilies. She was the life of the
OL,14,Fcommunity."
OL,16,FThere have been torturous waits
OL,17,Foutside the hospital, where
OL,18,Fauthorities are carrying out the task
OL,19,Fof identifying the bodies.
