OL,7,F"And this is what hurts us the most.
OL,8,FGive us answers."
OL,10,FA Foreign Office spokesperson said
OL,11,Fthere is reception centre at a nearby
OL,12,Fhotel and a helpline, but the families
OL,13,Fwants a British representative at the
OL,14,Fhospital.
OL,16,FForeign Office Minister Hamish
OL,17,FFalconer said: "I understand how
OL,18,Ffrustrating it is for families who
OL,19,Fhave not yet been able to lay their
OL,20,Floved ones to rest
